Actress Juliet Ibrahim has revealed that as a single lady, she cannot live without her sex toys.
Ibrahim disclosed this in her latest post where she flaunted her ‘rabbit sex toy’. The actress listed this as one of the ten things she is obsessed with and cannot live without. According to her, this is a must have for single ladies and keeps her company. She also revealed that she is an asthmatic patient. “As a single lady, a sex toy is a must have and it keeps me company. “It does everything I need,” she said.